oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Songwriter Session - Liz Rose - 2018-06-30
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Performance by songwriter Liz Rose from the Ford Theater at the Country Music Hall of Fame and Museum on June 30, 2018. Accompanied on guitar by Phil Barton.
